These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, plum, grapefruit, strawberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, classical, house
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, canadian, malaysian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle, fish, guinea-pig
 1. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 2. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
 3. the thai is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 4. the malaysian is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 5. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 7. the canadian is the person eating grapefruit##1
 8. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the fan of house##2
10. the person eating eggplant is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
11. the fan of classical is the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | grapefruit  | eggplant    | strawberry    | plum   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic     | blues   | classical       | house    |
| Nationality   | canadian | thai | turkish    | malaysian |
| Pet           | turtle | guinea-pig       | goldfish | fish     |

