.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, spinach, corn, apple
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, cooking, puzzles, dancing
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, brazilian, thai
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, sailing, badminton, weightlifting
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
 2. the japanese is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 4. the person eating spinach is the american##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 6. the american is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 7. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 8. the thai is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 9. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4
11. the brazilian is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | orange  | spinach    | corn     | apple       |
| Hobby         | puzzles | dancing | sudoku   | cooking |
| Nationality   | brazilian | american   | japanese   | thai    |
| Sport         | badminton | weightlifting  | skateboarding | sailing   |

