.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, water, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, doctor, bartender, musician
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, brazilian, polish, french
4 different pets are kept: turtle, rat, lizard, horse
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
 2. the brazilian is the bartender##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 4. the entrepreneur is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the musician##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is the french##1
 8. the musician is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking water is on the left of the nigerian##1
10. the owner of the turtle is the person drinking water##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | water   | milk    | iced-tea      |
| Job           | bartender | entrepreneur | doctor | musician     |
| Nationality   | brazilian      | french   | nigerian   | polish |
| Pet           | horse         | turtle       | lizard  | rat       |

