.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, lemon, watermelon, pear
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, baking, reading, rock-climbing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, soccer, volleyball, basketball
 1. the person drinking coffee is the person eating raspberry##1
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 8. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is baking##1
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating pear##1
12. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate       | mirinda   | coffee   | soy-milk   |
| Food       | lemon        | pear | raspberry    | watermelon       |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing | baking    | reading  | board-games |
| Sport      | soccer  | volleyball  | water-polo | basketball    |

