.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, peas, pepper, lemon
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, cooking, singing, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, teacher, architect, coach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, baseball, tennis
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person eating lemon##2
 3. the architect is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the teacher is the person eating apricot##1
 5. the pilot is on the left or right of the teacher##3
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating peas is the pilot##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is the teacher##1
 9. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
10. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3
12. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | pepper    | lemon      | apricot          | peas    |
| Hobby   | cooking | reading       | singing | drawing |
| Job     | coach     | architect      | teacher     | pilot |
| Sport   | rowing   | tennis | baseball        | badminton   |

