.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, hot-chocolate, water
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, blueberry, tomato, raspberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, disco, reggae, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, indonesian, russian, chinese
 1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 3. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 5. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of pop is between the russian and the fan of disco##2
 7. the fan of reggae is the person eating tomato##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is the person eating tomato##1
 9. the indonesian is on the far right##1
10. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate  | fanta    | sprite       | water       |
| Food          | raspberry    | tomato | blueberry | cranberry     |
| Music-Genre   | house | reggae        | pop    | disco   |
| Nationality   | turkish  | russian      | chinese    | indonesian |

