 7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
10. the brazilian is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
12. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
