 3. the colombian is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the polish is on the right of the french##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the italian##1
 9. the owner of the cat is between the colombian and the person watching documentary movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
12. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3

