The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, cycling, climbing, sailing
 1. the person eating carrot is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of punk is between the person watching animation movies and the person who's sport is cycling##2
 4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 6. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is the person watching animation movies##1
 9. the person eating artichoke is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
11. the person eating artichoke is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
13. the fan of techno is on the right of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
