There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, italian, colombian, british
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, weightlifting, baseball, cricket
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 3. the engineer is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is swimming##2
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the british##1
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
 8. the british is on the right of the colombian##1
 9. the accountant is on the left of the engineer##1
10. the manager is in an even position##4
11. the mexican is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | coffee      | almond-milk           | iced-tea |
| Job           | accountant | engineer | entrepreneur | manager        |
| Nationality   | colombian      | british  | mexican          | italian      |
| Sport         | cricket       | baseball    | swimming       | weightlifting       |

