 7. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
 8. the firefighter is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
10. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
12. the journalist is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
