 3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk       | coffee | sprite        | cola        |
| Hobby         | hiking | traveling       | dancing | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster     | animation        | comedy    | superhero      |
| Sport         | rugby     | biathlon    | swimming | climbing   |

