.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, reggae, d&b, folk
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, canadian, malaysian, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, lacrosse, weightlifting, golf
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, trike, airplane, bus
 1. the fan of folk is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the nigerian and the pakistani##2
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the canadian##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 6. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 8. the pakistani is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the nigerian is in an even position##4
11. the nigerian is on the far right##1
12. the fan of rock is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | rock | folk     | d&b        |
| Nationality   | malaysian | pakistani  | canadian     | nigerian |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | snowboarding | weightlifting      | golf |
| Transport     | bus | trike     | airplane | subway       |

 